      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Governing equations and constitutive models (turbulence, hemolysis power-law) justified relative to flow regime and COU requirements.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on prior literature for internal rotating flows. However, the hemolysis power-law coefficients (Giersiepen et al.) were not re-calibrated for the specific blood analogue used in bench testing; sensitivity of NIH predictions to coefficient uncertainty was not quantified. Model form justification is incomplete. Achieved level 1 is below required level 2."
    },
