      "rationale": "CAD geometry sourced from FDA GCBP repository (Rev 3). Blood analogue viscosity measured at 37°C; density from literature. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements. Input uncertainty table provided. Required level 2 met."
