    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD model for the CPB hemolysis COU at MRL 2. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; four factors achieved levels below their required levels (Discretization error, Test conditions, Model form, and a minor shortfall noted in input traceability). The team judged the overall body of evidence sufficient to support the Accepted outcome, citing the conservative RH < 1 acceptance criterion and the availability of physical testing as a confirmatory measure. No formal remediation plan was documented for the shortfall factors.",
